00:31:32,682 --> 00:31:34,392
I know a place
that might be open.

541
00:31:40,857 --> 00:31:42,734
Haven't been here in years.

542
00:31:44,277 --> 00:31:46,113
You know what this place
makes me think of?

543
00:31:46,696 --> 00:31:48,990
Hard lemonade
