just keep it around
for Mr. Paper.

571
00:33:22,250 --> 00:33:24,376
Got it, who's next?

572
00:33:24,377 --> 00:33:26,962
Thank you so much, thank you.

573
00:33:26,963 --> 00:33:28,590
Okay, bye.

