I think it's going well, Chad?

585
00:34:55,468 --> 00:34:59,054
I'm gonna stop by the bank later
and talk shop with the suits.

586
00:34:59,055 --> 00:35:01,932
Thanks, babe, I mean so much.

587
00:35:01,933 --> 00:35:03,560
