no more photos.

617
00:36:39,572 --> 00:36:41,990
Oh, well,
I wasn't charging for these.

618
00:36:41,991 --> 00:36:45,744
Yeah, but it cost money
to use them,

619
00:36:45,745 --> 00:36:50,124
ads, marketing materials,
printing cost, ah, it adds up.

620
00:36:50,125 --> 00:36:54,045
Well, you can still keep
the photos in, use them later.

621
00:36:54,713 --> 00:36:59,050
I guess you're not understanding,
look, no more photos.

622
00:37:00,301 --> 00:37:03,095
Okay, the thing
